      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.gY3X6RQyqwjMVTkC]{Vital (Niche)}</p>\n<p>You move with an exceptional burst of speed. As a swift action, you take a guarded step and gain a +1 enhancement bonus to your AC and Reflex saves until the beginning of your next turn. If you spend 2 MP when activating this evolution, you can instead move up to half your speed with the guarded step and the enhancement bonus increases to +2.</p>\n<p><em>Enable/disable active modifiers in the Modifiers tab.</em></p>"
